snippet.title: Circle of Sumo: Online Rumble! Official Trailer [Nintendo Switch]
snippet.description:
Circle of Sumo: Online Rumble! is an online multiplayer, competitive, fast-paced game, up to 4 players in which you fight as a Sumotori for the supremacy on the ring. The goal is to throw out the other players with a powerful belly-shot!

Circle of Sumo: Online Rumble! is now available on 
Nintendo Switch 
and Steam  https://bit.ly/3dvsr4l

The game is the online and FREE version of the classic Circle Of Sumo (already available on Nintendo Switch and Steam) 
Watch trailer: https://bit.ly/3lNwifO

Follow us on

Discord: https://discord.gg/vHpyBCS
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/CircleOfSumo/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/CircleOf_
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/circleofsumo/
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/CircleOfSumo/
